Package: escons
Title: Simulate seat allocation using survey data
Version: 0.0.6
Authors@R: 
    person(given="Gonzalo",
    family="Rivero",
    middle=NULL,
    email="me@griverorz.net",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functionality to make simulations of seat allocations
             using vote shares from survey data. The package is designed for use with Baròmetre
             data from the Centre d'Estudis d'Opinió. 
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests: 
    tinytest
